The flag-bearer of the Labour Party, Peter Obi, has promised to address Nigerians following the outcome of 2023 presidential elections. He disclosed this on his verified Twitter handle on Wednesday. “Our Vice presidential candidate Dr. Yusuf Datti Baba-Ahmed is addressing an international press conference at the Labour Party Headquarters in Abuja. I intend to address Nigerians and the international community shortly,” he tweeted.  